workflow.name: YouTube comment analysis with GPT-4o & automated email reports via Gmail
workflow.description:
**Description:**

Leverage the power of ChatGPT and YouTube API to monitor, analyze, and report on video feedback automatically. This n8n automation template fetches comments from a YouTube video, performs advanced AI sentiment analysis, identifies key themes, and emails a professional report‚Äîall triggered from a Google Sheet.

**What This Template Does:**

- üîÅ Auto-Triggers from Google Sheets every minute
- üé• Fetches YouTube video details and top comments
- üß† Uses GPT-4o for comment sentiment analysis, theme detection, viewer questions & improvement insights
- üìß Generates and sends an HTML email report with all key insights
- üìù Marks videos as ‚ÄúMail Sent‚Äù in the sheet to prevent duplicate reports

**Setup Requirements:**

- YouTube API Credentials
- OpenAI API Credentials 
- Gmail credentials for email delivery
- Google Sheet with video tracking

**Ideal for:**

YouTube creators, marketers, social media analysts, or agencies seeking automated YouTube comment sentiment analysis and actionable content insights‚Äîwithout writing a line of code.

nodes.name: Limit
nodes.notes: Limits processing to 1 item at a time to prevent API overload

nodes.name: AI Agent
nodes.notes: Uses OpenAI GPT-4o to analyze comments and generate insights. Customize the prompt for different analysis needs.

nodes.name: If
nodes.notes: Filters rows to process only videos with 'Pending' status

nodes.name: Set Video Details
nodes.notes: Prepares video ID and sets max comments limit (100)

nodes.name: Get Youtube Video Details
nodes.notes: Fetches video metadata including title, channel name, and other details

nodes.name: Get Youtube Video Comments
nodes.notes: Retrieves top 100 comments ordered by relevance using YouTube API

nodes.name: Prepare Comments Data
nodes.notes: Processes raw comments: extracts text, calculates stats, performs basic sentiment analysis, limits to 50 comments for AI

nodes.name: Prepare HTML for Email
nodes.notes: Converts AI analysis into formatted HTML email with statistics, insights, and professional styling

nodes.name: Gmail Account Configuration
nodes.notes: Sends formatted analysis report via Gmail. Update SENDER_EMAIL_ADDRESS with actual recipient

nodes.name: Update Status on Google Sheet
nodes.notes: Updates video status to 'Mail Sent' to prevent duplicate processing

nodes.name: Pick Video Ids from Google sheet
nodes.notes: Triggers on new YouTube videos added to spreadsheet. Polls every minute for changes

data.details:
The IF node can be used to implement binary conditional logic in your workflow. You can set up one-to-many conditions to evaluate each item of data being inputted into the node. That data will either evaluate to TRUE or FALSE and route out of the node accordingly.

This node has multiple types of conditions: Bool, String, Number, and Date & Time.
